Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.02,0:00:11.03,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs55\pos(362.25,343)}Nodame Kantabile
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.40,0:01:26.61,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Betoven...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.91,0:01:34.20,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Zdravo.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.16,0:01:34.18,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(365.625,352)}Lekcija 14
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.61,0:01:36.21,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Ah?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.41,0:01:37.41,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Da?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.66,0:01:39.08,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Jeli to Saiko?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.83,0:01:42.25,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Ne... ovde Nodame.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.79,0:01:44.93,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Zar ovo nije Šiničijev mobilni?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.34,0:01:49.43,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Šiniči... Tu je, tu je...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.68,0:01:50.97,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Šiniči.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.09,0:01:51.96,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Telefon.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.35,0:01:53.26,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Budi se.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.89,0:01:55.38,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Hajde, probudi se.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.39,0:01:58.14,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Ko je?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.77,0:01:59.48,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Jeli to Šiniči?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.31,0:02:01.77,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Odmah se vraćaj.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.22,0:02:03.02,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Ujače Takeja.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.15,0:02:05.28,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Povedi tu devojku sa sobom i odmah se vraćaj.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.78,0:02:06.61,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,To je naređenje.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.03,0:02:07.65,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Razumeš?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.16,0:02:13.20,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Ko je zvao?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.24,0:02:16.50,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Z-Zašto sam ja u tvojoj sobi?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.75,0:02:19.75,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Eh, ne sećaš se?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.12,0:02:25.30,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Posle žurke si rekao "Želim da sednem za kotacu i pijem!" pa si došao kod mene
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.46,0:02:27.09,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,i pio i pevao celu noć.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.58,0:02:30.59,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Onda smo plesali valcer.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.59,0:02:33.76,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, opet je jutro?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.85,0:02:36.31,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, moj bože...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.64,0:02:41.27,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Mislio sam da će me uskoro zvati,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.94,0:02:44.31,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,ali nisam očekivao ovakav tajming.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.31,0:02:48.35,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Čiaki, kako mi stoji ovo?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.15,0:02:51.20,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Š-Šta je to?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.41,0:02:53.22,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Šminka kako bi mi lice izgledalo manje.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.32,0:02:56.54,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Pošto idem da upoznam tvoju porodicu, moram pravilno da se spremim.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.74,0:02:57.62,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Šta je tu pravilno!?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.12,0:03:01.42,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Hoću li se svideti tvojim roditeljima?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.08,0:03:04.58,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Zašto moram i nju da vodim?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.95,0:03:07.55,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Sigurno nas je pogrešno shvatio.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.37,0:03:09.34,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Skidaj šminku.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.67,0:03:10.38,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Molim te.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.92,0:03:14.64,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,I takođe... pošto su moji roditelji razvedeni,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.71,0:03:17.59,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,sada idemo kod moje majke,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.43,0:03:19.77,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,što je kuća mog ujaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.34,0:03:23.90,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Mijoši porodica se starala o meni od moje dvanaeste.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.90,0:03:33.57,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Ovo je tvoja...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.11,0:03:34.66,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Da.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.90,0:03:37.53,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Dobrodošao,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.91,0:03:39.29,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Šin, bato.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.33,0:03:41.04,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Juiko.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.41,0:03:42.46,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Bata!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.42,0:03:46.92,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Šin, bato, uželela sam te se!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.25,0:03:49.13,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Porasla si, Juiko.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.30,0:03:52.08,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Naravno. Prošla je cela godina.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.55,0:03:55.06,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,I ti si bato postao još divniji.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.50,0:03:56.55,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Pa, idemo.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.50,0:03:58.40,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,{\move(208.125,157,393.75,290)}Idi kući
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.01,0:03:58.42,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Svi te čekaju.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.76,0:04:00.35,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Ovaj... Čiaki-
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.19,0:04:08.98,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Bre, nikada me ne zoveš.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.52,0:04:12.69,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,A i izabrao si karijeru a da se nisi posavetovao sa mnom.
Dialogue: 1,0:04:12.65,0:04:18.37,Nodame imena,,0,0,0,,{\pos(534.375,318)}Korporacija Mijoši
Dialogue: 1,0:04:12.65,0:04:18.37,Nodame imena,,0,0,0,,{\pos(537.75,344)}Potpredsednik
Dialogue: 1,0:04:12.65,0:04:18.37,Nodame imena,,0,0,0,,{\pos(537.75,372)}Takehiko Mijoši (50 god.)
Dialogue: 2,0:04:13.37,0:04:18.41,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Šta misliš čija je zasluga što možeš da studiraš muziku bez ikakve brige?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:18.37,0:04:23.20,Nodame imena,,0,0,0,,{\pos(558,353)}Prva ćerka, Juiko, 10 god.
Dialogue: 2,0:04:18.78,0:04:19.79,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Zahvaljujući tebi.
Dialogue: 2,0:04:20.04,0:04:21.04,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Izvinjavam se zbog toga.
Dialogue: 2,0:04:21.45,0:04:23.25,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Šin, bato, praviš se važan.
Dialogue: 1,0:04:23.21,0:04:26.07,Nodame imena,,0,0,0,,{\pos(564.75,360)}Prvi sin, Tošihiko, 14 god.
Dialogue: 2,0:04:24.24,0:04:29.00,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Nije da me zanima, ali, brate, nije li ono tvoja devojka?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.80,0:04:36.09,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Brate, tvoj ukus se promenio.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.34,0:04:37.47,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Previše!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.97,0:04:39.93,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Šta se desilo sa Saiko?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.98,0:04:40.84,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,To je nesporazum!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.84,0:04:41.93,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Šta je nesporazum?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.23,0:04:48.06,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Ovaj... izvoli, uđi.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.27,0:04:52.28,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Drago mi je.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.39,0:04:54.65,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Ja sam Megumi Noda.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.82,0:04:59.03,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Šiniči mi uvek daje hrane i veliki sam mu dužnik.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.53,0:05:01.33,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Ja sam sluškinja.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.71,0:05:03.86,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Zato što trebam o nečemu da pričam sa Šiničijem.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.28,0:05:06.07,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Zato što trebam da učim.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.37,0:05:07.53,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Osećaj se kao kod kuće.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.37,0:05:07.53,Nodame Alternativa,,0,0,0,,Osećaj se kao kod kuće.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.41,0:05:10.34,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Kao kod kuće...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.63,0:05:17.34,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Tošihiko,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.26,0:05:19.93,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,hoćeš da zajedno sviramo violinu posle?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.43,0:05:21.51,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Ja ću te pratiti na klaviru.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.44,0:05:24.18,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Neka.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.68,0:05:26.31,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Prestao sam da sviram violinu.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.56,0:05:28.05,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Eh? Zašto?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.44,0:05:29.15,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Zašto...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.27,0:05:31.06,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Nije bitno.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.82,0:05:34.78,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Ne sviram pošto ne želim da sviram.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.40,0:05:38.41,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Tako znači.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.24,0:05:43.95,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Ali ne vole svi muziku kao što je ti voliš.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.49,0:05:44.87,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Aha.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.54,0:05:50.29,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Nekada je toliko voleo violinu.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.67,0:05:53.63,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Uvek me je pratio svuda.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.88,0:05:56.51,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Zato što te je mnogo voleo.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.88,0:05:59.34,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Znači sada me mrzi?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.93,0:06:02.76,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Sada je u teškim godinama. Ostavi ga na miru.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.64,0:06:07.51,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Ali u zadnje vreme se baš bacio na učenje.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.98,0:06:12.02,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Pretpostavljam da je konačno shvatio da je naslednik Mijoši korporacije.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.56,0:06:17.90,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Pa, ocene su mu konačno u prvih deset, i to je tek početak.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.32,0:06:21.16,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Zar nije dovoljno što je u prvih deset u prestižnoj školi?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.57,0:06:23.41,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Ja sam uvek bio prvi.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.94,0:06:24.83,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Ovaj čovek...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.45,0:06:27.36,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Ali danas sam hteo da popričamo o tebi.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.33,0:06:30.67,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,N-Nego, gde su moja majka i ujna Čiharu?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.92,0:06:33.42,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Seiko je na kulturnom poslovnom putu u inostranstvu,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.75,0:06:36.13,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,a Čiharu je otišla sa njom da se zabavi.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.76,0:06:38.34,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Zdravo.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.67,0:06:39.42,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Nije valjda.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.34,0:06:41.68,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Izgleda da razumeš.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.18,0:06:44.10,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Upoznaću te.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.60,0:06:47.97,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Ovo je svetski poznat stručnjak za hipnozu,
Dialogue: 1,0:06:47.75,0:06:50.80,Nodame objasnjenje,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,300)\pos(505.125,327)}Hipnotizer
Dialogue: 1,0:06:47.75,0:06:50.80,Nodame objasnjenje,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,300)\pos(505.125,367)}Gert Fišer
Dialogue: 2,0:06:48.52,0:06:50.85,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Gert Fišer.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.05,0:06:52.06,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Guten tag!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.15,0:06:55.15,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Ponovo... znao sam.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.78,0:07:07.37,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Neverovatno... tako brzo su se sprijateljile.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.74,0:07:11.54,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Juiko koja je obično teška se toliko smeje.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.51,0:07:25.55,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Jeli u redu ako ne legnem na krevet?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.85,0:07:29.02,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,U redu je, dokle god si opušten.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.27,0:07:29.72,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Jesam.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.73,0:07:32.60,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Čini mi se da si se navikao na ovo.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.19,0:07:35.81,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Ovo mi je treća terapija hipnozom.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.19,0:07:37.07,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Toliko puta?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.36,0:07:39.64,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Nije uspelo ni jednom.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.82,0:07:42.99,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Prošli put je bio psihički medijum.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.11,0:07:44.70,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Pre toga su bile bajalice i molitve.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.62,0:07:47.41,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Čim nema majke, odmah dođe do ovoga.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.78,0:07:51.36,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Pošto hipnoza nije magija ili psihička sposobnost,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.07,0:07:54.71,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,ponekad radi, a ponekad ne radi.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.00,0:07:56.04,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Nije savršena.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.79,0:08:01.04,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Doktore, jeste li ikada izlečili pacijenta kao što sam ja?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.30,0:08:01.97,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Jesam.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.47,0:08:04.97,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Strah od aviona i brodova.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.97,0:08:06.19,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Samo dvoje, doduše.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.80,0:08:07.51,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Čak toliko.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.67,0:08:11.10,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Hoćeš li mi ispričati svoju priču?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.48,0:08:15.05,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Ti si student, zar ne?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.35,0:08:17.81,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Kakav je studentski život?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.43,0:08:20.53,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Haos je.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.94,0:08:23.07,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Zadnjih godinu ipo dana,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.19,0:08:25.36,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,juri me jedna uvrnuta devojka.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.61,0:08:28.99,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Ona je toliko čudna da biste mogli i nju malo da pogledate.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.36,0:08:31.37,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Živi u stanu do mene.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.58,0:08:33.50,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Njen stan je uvek prljav kao kanta za otpatke.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.00,0:08:37.96,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Ponekad je i sama smrdljiva, i šta je sa time?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.63,0:08:42.34,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Iako je žensko, mrzi da se kupa i danima nosi istu odeću.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.67,0:08:46.51,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Čak i ako je lenja, trebala bi bar da se uredi pred muškarcem koji joj se sviđa.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.84,0:08:48.34,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Danas je najgore.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.76,0:08:52.02,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Došlo je do nesporazuma da mi je ona devojka i morao sam da je povedem sa sobom.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.39,0:08:57.51,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Zašto li sam je doveo?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.06,0:09:00.73,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Mogao sam da ignorišem to.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.15,0:09:04.85,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Slušate li me?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.70,0:09:07.61,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Uopšte ga nisam hipnotisao.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.20,0:09:10.25,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Ne vredi, kao što sam i mislio.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.99,0:09:13.75,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Zato i kažem da hipnoza ne radi na meni.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.08,0:09:15.57,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Pa šta onda radi?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.62,0:09:16.32,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Reci mi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.17,0:09:21.38,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Reći ću ti iskreno.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.38,0:09:23.21,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Zašto više ne ostaviš muziku?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.80,0:09:29.39,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Čak i ako si talentovan, ako ne možeš da napustiš Japan, nema ti druge.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.75,0:09:30.85,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Ako ne možeš da izađeš u svet...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.10,0:09:32.89,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,I u Japanu mogu da se bavim muzikom.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.26,0:09:35.22,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Centar klasične muzike je tamo.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.68,0:09:40.72,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Čak i ako si hvaljen u Japanu, ako nisi u svetu, ne možeš da budeš na vrhu.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.94,0:09:42.85,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Vrhu...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.53,0:09:46.53,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Tako sam i ja mislio ranije.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.70,0:09:48.56,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Ali sada...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.44,0:09:51.91,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Čak ni u Japanu nisam još ništa...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.44,0:09:54.24,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Tu strast uloži u moju kompaniju.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.42,0:10:07.42,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Ko je učinio ovo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.13,0:10:08.55,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Izvoli.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.29,0:10:09.63,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Ha?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.47,0:10:12.63,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,J-Ja sam.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.10,0:10:15.26,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Jesi li ti dete?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.88,0:10:19.47,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Trebala bi da si primetila da će odleteti tamo ako je udariš odavde.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.32,0:10:21.56,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,I-Izvini.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.73,0:10:23.56,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,I ti sebe zoveš odraslom osobom.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.65,0:10:25.15,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,I kakve su to ogrebotine?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.73,0:10:27.07,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Šta ste to radile?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.69,0:10:28.81,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Bejzbol i...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.99,0:10:31.57,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Takmičenje u skakanju... sa visokog brda...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.70,0:10:32.37,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Ha?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.87,0:10:34.87,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! Moj Koimari!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.87,0:10:35.99,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Bizen...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.12,0:10:37.16,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Majzen...
Comment: 0,0:10:32.87,0:10:37.16,Nodame objasnjenje,,0,0,0,,Koimari, Bizen, Majzen - skupa keramika
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.16,0:10:37.95,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Idemo kući, Nodame.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.20,0:10:38.61,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.66,0:10:39.46,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Nije "Eh?".
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.91,0:10:41.08,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Ne možemo više ovde da ostanemo.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.38,0:10:47.92,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Ne, nemoj da ideš!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.04,0:10:50.42,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Šin-bato, Nodame.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.09,0:10:52.25,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Nemojte da idete!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.13,0:10:58.98,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Zašto?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.64,0:11:02.73,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Zašto je ova kuća...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.48,0:11:05.86,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Ova kuća nije bila ovakva.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.08,0:11:10.42,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Šiniči, možeš li da odsviraš San Sans?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.79,0:11:16.46,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Ova kuća je uvek bila puna muzike.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.76,0:11:20.63,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Šin-bata, koji je uvek svirao note od zlata,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.79,0:11:24.26,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,je bio ponos mog dede, koji je voleo muziku.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.14,0:11:27.22,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Želeo sam da budem kao Šin-bata.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.13,0:11:32.65,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Dete ne okleva da pomisli da može da postane vanzemaljac ili druge stvari kada poraste.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.36,0:11:37.69,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Opet mi se širi brada.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.39,0:11:39.60,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Mladi gospodine Tošihiko,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.49,0:11:42.07,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,večera je spremna.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.24,0:11:44.28,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Barem pokucaj pre nego što uđeš.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.57,0:11:45.74,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Jesam pokucala.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.86,0:11:47.29,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Bio si koncentrisan na bradu...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.33,0:11:49.75,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Zar se nisi vratila kući?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.95,0:11:53.83,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Spremila sam večeru kao izvinjenje za polomljene vaze.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.72,0:11:55.23,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\pos(605.25,207)}Оdrađuje štetu
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.16,0:11:55.26,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Slobodno se posluži.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.20,0:11:57.66,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Razumem, idi više.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.91,0:11:58.96,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Sići ću uskoro.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.34,0:12:01.58,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, strava.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.76,0:12:03.63,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Kakav veliki monitor.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.47,0:12:05.68,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Ovaj font je...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.21,0:12:07.56,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Ne gledaj!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.72,0:12:10.22,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Ne mogu da verujem.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.52,0:12:12.80,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Jesi li ti stvarno njegova devojka?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.05,0:12:15.06,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Nemaš takta i nisi privlačna.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.35,0:12:16.52,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Kakav ukus on ima?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.77,0:12:20.74,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Jesu li kompjuteri tvoj hobi?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.49,0:12:22.73,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Hobi?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.19,0:12:26.23,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,U današnje vreme je čudno kada nemaš kompjuter.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.82,0:12:29.87,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Očeva kompanija se bavi informacionim tehnologijama.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.12,0:12:32.49,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,I on se nekad specijalizovao u toj oblasti.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.12,0:12:35.03,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Čak i ja...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.74,0:12:40.13,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Jedine klasične stvari ovde su ova kuća i Šiniči.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.21,0:12:43.47,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Zahvalan sam na večeri.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.84,0:12:45.13,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Stvarno jesam, ali...
Comment: 0,0:12:46.72,0:12:48.72,Nodame objasnjenje,,0,0,0,,Mizutaki - kuvano jelo koje se obično jede zimi
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.72,0:12:48.72,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Ali zašto Mizutaki, iako je proleće?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.92,0:12:52.27,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Gospođica Nodame je rekla da nikada nije omanula u pripremi kuvanih jela.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.73,0:12:54.22,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Ko ovo zove pripremanjem?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.22,0:12:56.65,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Hajde, hajde, poslužite se.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.85,0:12:58.98,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Nikada nisam omanula u pripremi onigirija.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.98,0:13:00.15,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Teško je da se dohvati.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.20,0:13:02.32,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Dajte za svakog odvojeno, kao i uvek.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.44,0:13:05.36,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Gospođica Nodame je rekla da Nabe treba svi da dele.
Comment: 0,0:13:02.44,0:13:07.78,Nodame objasnjenje,,0,0,0,,Nabe - zajednički naziv za razna japanska kuvana jela koja se obično jedu iz jedne posude (nabe - lonac)
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.07,0:13:07.78,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Tata, hajde mi dohvati.
Comment: 0,0:13:07.78,0:13:14.12,Nodame objasnjenje,,0,0,0,,Širataki - vrsta japanskih testenina
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.78,0:13:09.49,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Ja hoću tofu i širataki.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.28,0:13:14.12,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... aha, dohvatiću ti. Tofu i širataki, jel?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.32,0:13:15.83,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,I tebi, Tošihiko, ću da dohvatim.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.03,0:13:16.53,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Šta želiš?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.12,0:13:21.75,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Odavno nismo ovako večerali svi zajedno.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.59,0:13:24.80,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Ja sam retko bio kući jer sam bio zauzet.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.13,0:13:29.05,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Prilično opušteno podnosiš to što je majka pobegla od kuće.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.05,0:13:32.13,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, ovaj račić je ukusan!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.18,0:13:33.10,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Gde ste ga kupili?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.35,0:13:35.31,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Nisi ga valjda ti spremila sama?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.89,0:13:40.68,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Gospodin Šiniči ga je spremio pošto nije mogao da stoji besposlen.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.77,0:13:42.98,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Gospođo Čijo, zamolio sam vas da ne otkrijete.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.48,0:13:45.28,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... Šiniči.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.90,0:13:49.78,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Ti uvek nadmašiš druge, šta god uzeo da radiš.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.20,0:13:53.37,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Čak i u učenju i plesanju je tako.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.74,0:13:56.96,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Hoćeš li ipak da ostaviš muziku, i radiš za moju kompaniju?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.53,0:14:01.25,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Ti bi sigurno mogao brzo da postaneš moja desnica.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.34,0:14:05.21,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Ako od mene oduzmete muziku, neće ostati ništa.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.72,0:14:07.34,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Nisam toliko vešt.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.88,0:14:11.39,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,A i nameravam da napravim novi orkestar
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.98,0:14:13.93,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,i imam planove i ciljeve.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.38,0:14:15.68,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Novi orkestar?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.09,0:14:17.10,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Šta je sa time?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.35,0:14:18.52,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Hoćeš li sam da ga napraviš?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.10,0:14:21.86,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Sakupiću vešte članove i održati koncert.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.99,0:14:23.15,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,A sponzor?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.32,0:14:25.19,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Za sada ga nemam, ali ću smisliti nešto.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.94,0:14:28.40,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Tek treba da počnem.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.49,0:14:30.45,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Znači amaterski orkestar je u pitanju.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.87,0:14:32.53,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Kakva je korist od toga?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.99,0:14:36.25,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Mnogo bi bolje bilo da učestvuješ u takmičenju u dirigovanju.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.58,0:14:38.50,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Zar ne želiš da postaneš profesionalac?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.50,0:14:39.53,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Postaću, jednog dana!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.83,0:14:40.96,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Kada će to biti?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.16,0:14:47.67,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Brate, ti si učenik Sebastijana Viere, zar ne?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.97,0:14:49.68,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Kada ćeš se videti sa njime?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.13,0:14:52.21,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Kada ne možeš da uđeš u avion ili na brod!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.93,0:14:56.81,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Ne može...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.93,0:14:59.55,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Otkriven sam.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.60,0:15:03.69,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Kao što je moj otac rekao, trebao bi da se pridružiš našoj kompaniji.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.98,0:15:05.86,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Tebi ništa ne bi bilo nemoguće.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.28,0:15:08.69,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Pošto si, za razliku od mene, pametan, vešt
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.15,0:15:12.04,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,i harizmatičan, savršen si naslednik.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.04,0:15:12.82,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Tošihiko.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.37,0:15:15.37,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Možda ne znaš...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.53,0:15:20.21,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,ali ranije je bio plan da te udrogiraju i odnesu u inostranstvo.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.87,0:15:22.12,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Prekini, Tošihiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.38,0:15:25.84,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Ali auto u kojem si bio je učestvovao u lančanom sudaru,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.88,0:15:30.38,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,a avion kojim si trebao da letiš je morao da se vrati na aerodrom zbog mehaničkih problema.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.84,0:15:33.05,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Sigurno si uklet.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.30,0:15:34.30,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Tošihiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.89,0:15:37.26,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Ako želiš da Šiniči radi za Mijoši,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.26,0:15:39.98,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,trebao bi direktno da mu kažeš umesto što uvijaš!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.22,0:15:41.89,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Prijatno.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.82,0:15:57.08,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Ionako se niko ne brine za mene.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.40,0:16:00.16,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Svi me ignorišu...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.96,0:16:02.67,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Čak i moj deda i otac...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.62,0:16:05.88,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Niko ni ne pokušava da me uporedi sa Šiničijem.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.30,0:16:11.58,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Nodame, hajde da spavamo zajedno.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.13,0:16:13.22,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Nemoj da se vraćaš kući.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.59,0:16:17.30,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Ne brini, dozvolili su mi da ostanem preko noći.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.76,0:16:19.22,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,A i onako sada više ne mogu da se vratim.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.31,0:16:21.18,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Hvala ti.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.68,0:16:23.69,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Hoćemo da se kupamo zajedno?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.15,0:16:25.90,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Pošto smo se toliko igrale danas?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.98,0:16:28.77,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Nodame.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.44,0:16:33.11,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Moja mama će da se vrati, zar ne?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.27,0:16:35.91,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Neće da se razvedu, zar ne?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.24,0:16:38.62,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Mama je rekla
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.54,0:16:43.96,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,otkako je deda preminuo, vazduh u ovoj kući je postao ustajao.
Comment: 0,0:16:42.87,0:16:43.91,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(186.75,89)}Тухлый
Comment: 0,0:16:42.87,0:16:43.91,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(191.25,153)}Затхлый
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.28,0:16:45.62,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Rekla je da ne može da se diše...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.21,0:16:49.71,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Onda je možda samo otišla da se odmori malo.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.25,0:16:54.04,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,I meni je zagušljivo kada dugo ostanem u svojoj sobi,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.04,0:16:56.14,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,pa zato često bežim od kuće.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.14,0:16:57.64,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,U sobu Šin-bate.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.64,0:17:00.31,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Eh? To nije fer!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.91,0:17:17.70,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Noćna mora.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.62,0:17:20.28,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Nisam je davno video.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.04,0:17:22.29,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,A i šta je to bilo?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.83,0:17:23.91,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Nikada ga nisam video ranije.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.57,0:17:25.46,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Ljudsko biće?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.87,0:17:27.71,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Sigurno si uklet, brate.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.08,0:17:29.84,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Zato što je rekao tako nešto.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.50,0:17:31.96,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Dovraga!
Dialogue: 1,0:17:52.27,0:17:57.19,Nodame imena,,0,0,0,,{\pos(194.625,340)}Johan Sebastijan Bah
Dialogue: 1,0:17:52.27,0:17:57.19,Nodame imena,,0,0,0,,{\pos(199.125,388)}Pasija po Mateju
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.90,0:18:04.50,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Šta je bilo, Šiniči?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.66,0:18:06.82,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Jesi li opet sanjao strašan san?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.16,0:18:10.46,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Onda, hoćeš li zajedno da slušamo muziku?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.21,0:18:15.83,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Pasija po Mateju
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.08,0:18:17.26,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Ovo je Bah, zar ne?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.63,0:18:20.68,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Retko je da ti, Čiaki, slušaš neku pesmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.46,0:18:22.60,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Kako si to obučena?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.72,0:18:23.72,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, ovo?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.26,0:18:27.02,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Izgleda da je ovo spavaćica tvoje majke.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.27,0:18:28.98,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Zar ne izgledam kao princeza?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.76,0:18:32.85,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Ali ova audio soba je neverovatna.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.36,0:18:36.32,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Ovde ima toliko ploča i partitura.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.82,0:18:38.36,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Ovo je soba mog preminulog dede.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.32,0:18:41.03,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,On je strastveno voleo muziku
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.57,0:18:43.28,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,i svirao čelo kao hobi.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.69,0:18:45.04,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, čelo.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.74,0:18:49.28,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Pa, jel svirao zajedno sa tobom?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.75,0:18:50.74,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Često.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.45,0:18:59.26,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Dedini prijatelji, muzičari, su se često skupljali i održavali koncerte u salonu ove kuće nekada.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.88,0:19:00.56,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Salon?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.93,0:19:04.81,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Pa, to je prošlost, do pre pet godina.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.88,0:19:08.89,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Tada je u ovoj kući stalno bilo muzike.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.89,0:19:14.27,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Vau, 60 kompleta Hajfecovih CD-ova.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.11,0:19:16.53,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Da li da ih ponesem sa sobom?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.78,0:19:18.15,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Eno je Milhijeva ploča.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.94,0:19:19.90,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Baš je mlad.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.49,0:19:21.86,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, Frank.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.29,0:19:26.08,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Ova sonata za violinu je ona koju je Maki izvodila skoro.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.32,0:19:28.50,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, Mine ju je svirao na ispitu.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.86,0:19:31.17,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,I deo za klavir je prilično dobar ovde.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.87,0:19:34.75,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Čiaki, u ovoj kući ima klavir, zar ne?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.79,0:19:36.91,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,I violina, takođe?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.42,0:19:38.59,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Ima ih, doduše.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.38,0:19:41.22,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Ozbiljna je.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.75,0:19:44.55,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Čekaj trenutak.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.21,0:19:46.97,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Ako ćemo da sviramo, ovo delo bi bilo dobro.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.59,0:19:52.14,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Ali ja ne znam ovo.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.60,0:19:57.11,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Imamo i partiture, ali tebi je dovoljno da je čuješ, zar ne?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.98,0:19:59.85,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Elgar?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.81,0:20:03.27,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Zašto me zoveš u ovo doba?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.61,0:20:04.70,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Razmisli o razlici u vremenu!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.78,0:20:06.66,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Sada je 5 ujutru u Japanu!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.12,0:20:09.36,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Zašto sada pričaš o nečemu tako važnom?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.75,0:20:11.79,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Zašto mi nisi rekao pre nego što se dogodilo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.66,0:20:13.33,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Šta?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.62,0:20:15.04,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Jesi li ti predsednik?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.04,0:20:16.08,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Prekini da se zavitlavaš!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.13,0:20:18.96,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Dovraga.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.30,0:20:22.08,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Svi me podcenjuju.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.88,0:20:25.64,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Ta prethodna generacija... zaostali su za vremenom.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.43,0:20:26.89,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Dovraga.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.89,0:20:29.88,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Da li je pedeset godina još mladost?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.43,0:20:33.73,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Uvek koristiš reči "ovih dana" i "najbolje".
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.14,0:20:36.27,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Gledaš samo ono što je pravo ispred tebe.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.81,0:20:39.36,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Ponekad bi trebao da pogledaš iza sebe.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.64,0:20:42.19,Nodame Default,,0,0,0,,Nisi li zaboravio nešto važno?
